### Calculate CI for population [__slope__]{style="color:green"} $\beta_1$

$$b_1 \pm t^*\cdot SE_{b_1}$$  

where $t^*$ is the $t$-distribution critical value with $df = n -2$.


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
tidy(model1, conf.int = TRUE) %>% gt()
```

